    <div id="applyModal" class="fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center p-4 modal hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/80 backdrop-blur-sm" id="closeApplyBg"></div>
        <div class="glass-modal w-full max-w-sm rounded-2xl p-6 relative transform transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">참가 신청</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mb-6">AI Explorer Club 가입을 위해<br>간단한 정보를 입력해주세요.</p>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-xs text-slate-400 mb-1">이름 (실명)</label>
                    <input type="text" id="userName" class="w-full bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-600 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder-slate-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-violet-500 transition-colors" placeholder="홍길동">
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-xs text-slate-400 mb-1">연락처 (전화번호 또는 이메일)</label>
                    <input type="text" id="userContact" class="w-full bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-600 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder-slate-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-violet-500 transition-colors" placeholder="010-1234-5678">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-6 flex gap-3">
                <button id="closeApplyBtn" class="flex-1 py-3 rounded-lg text-slate-400 bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 font-medium text-sm transition-colors">취소</button>
                <button id="submitApplyBtn" class="flex-1 py-3 rounded-lg text-white bg-violet-600 hover:bg-violet-500 font-bold text-sm shadow-lg shadow-violet-900/20 transition-colors">신청 완료</button>
